{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"734-lalela-umzimba-wami","title":"Lalela umzimba wami","description":"Each of us has a wonderful body. But have you ever listened to what it tells you?","language":"isiZulu","langCode":"zu","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Family Literacy Project"],"illustrators":["Angie & Upesh"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/734-lalela-umzimba-wami"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700895/size3/19ca6ebcfc082bc86d63cf3227d13b74.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700895/size6/19ca6ebcfc082bc86d63cf3227d13b74.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9211/size6/d69a115f0c159ea882793ba2cb41ff0a.jpg","text":"Namhlanje angiyi esikoleni.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9212/size6/e67202d3c0724d1ae12f5525d9dc8856.jpg","text":"Yiholide!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9213/size6/50b694506f146bcdb0646ca8053f7a51.jpg","text":"Namhlanje angeke ngiwubuke umabonakude.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9214/size6/b8e641dba09c099282edc58af00491cf.jpg","text":"Awukho ugesi.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9215/size6/3ecaea9bd358488c9ade06643ca1ecd5.jpg","text":"Ngizokwenzani? Namhlanje ngizolalela umzimba wami!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9216/size6/f3770f7efffc083fda79a2a9dfc12dc7.jpg","text":"Uyawuzwa umzimba wakho?","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9217/size6/afb864fb23f4c5a4b37f085b77998e93.jpg","text":"Okokuqala kumele ngithule, ngithulisise.\nUkuze ngilale umzimba wami.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9218/size6/fd74e5e6b88ab5328e4dc167ed19caa1.jpg","text":"Yebo , manje ngiyawuzwa umoya wami. Donsa…khipha… donsa…khipha…","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9219/size6/1c9e720d459b3ccf8cb58a0005633f99.jpg","text":"Futhi ngingawenza umoya ube nomsindo… Sssssssssssssss! Futhi ngingawenza ube phansi Mmmmmmmm.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9220/size6/e44035c6ff05d3c34ed2a3cb85a199f6.jpg","text":"Manje ngiyayizwa inhliziyo yami ishaya!\nDoodom,\ndoodoom,\ndooodooom.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9221/size6/b33e0cc792cac701dd5bee3c6516c8d8.jpg","text":"Ngingayenza inhliziyo yami ishaye ngamandla futhi ngokushesha?\nYebo ngingagxumagxuma kufikela kumashumi amabili.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9222/size6/1bbe179bec0c1fbc347d9ab5d699b2c7.jpg","text":"Awubheke inhliziyo yami isishaya ngamandla.\nDoodom,\ndoodoom,\ndooodooom!","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9223/size6/02ba00623563facb600ff79966b52b87.jpg","text":"Futhi uma ngibeka iminwe yami esihlakaleni, ngiyakuzwaukushaya kwegazi!","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9224/size6/1443c997d29cf44512d1146a698cd5be.jpg","text":"Futhi ngingazizwa ngihleka\nhaha\nhaha\nhaha\nhahahha!","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9225/size6/275fab1b0e972aa9d8056ed203866692.jpg","text":"Noma ngikhala\nBoohoooohooooo!","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9226/size6/65228cb2933cbaa00789deb9a4b0bb16.jpg","text":"Noma ngishaya izandla\ntap\ntappa\ntapppaaaa.","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9227/size6/e71f8fe4b9679488059ae940be347ec3.jpg","text":"Phezu kwako konke ngiyasizwa isisu sami sikhala\nguddduu gudddu …","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9228/size6/1274d06379e74a021d185815759b20e2.jpg","text":"Sithi, \"Ngiphe ukudla ,ngiphe ukudla.\"","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9229/size6/c8917f7ecb0112d31da482d8d6c9795f.jpg","text":"Ikhala lami liyalizwa iphunga ekhishini likamama?\nNgabe ikhala liyezwa?","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9230/size6/f8cd7c097e22a9bbb628b475b65ba8cc.jpg","text":"Kumnandi ukulalela umzimba wami!\nManje ngifuna ukuzwa imihlathi yami ihlafuna.","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/9231/size6/ece2e176e7eccf901f54a55093b6bf30.jpg","text":"Kumnandi ukulalela umzimba wami!\nManje ngifuna ukuzwa imihlathi yami ihlafuna.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":21,"words":141}}